participants.title: Looking to connect with high level Cyber Security Professionals

messages.message:
Long Term Development Contract - Orange County, CA

Hi Brian, 

I hope this message finds you well.

I wanted to reach out to you to introduce an exciting contract opportunity in Orange County. My client, a well respected Microsoft Gold Partner, are looking for strong .NET contractors, ideally with some exposure to .NET core.

The role is a 7 month contract starting on 1/4 with expectations of onsite 100% of the time in Orange County.

I would love to discuss full details with you at a time that is convenient; when works for you to discuss?

Thanks

Stuart Mitchell
+1 212 252 2067 | stuart.mitchell@elliottbrowne.com
Not interested in contracts, can you ask the CEO to hire me full time?
